visual_events.description: Inside the helicopter, showing the patient on a stretcher with medical equipment and two medical personnel.
View from the helicopter window showing a grassy field with trees and a few vehicles in the distance, indicating a landing or takeoff zone.
Inside the helicopter, showing the medical personnel attending to the patient, with one person looking at a monitor displaying vital signs.
View from the helicopter window as it takes off, showing the ground receding and green fields with trees.
One medical personnel looking out the window, observing the landscape as the helicopter ascends.
Medical personnel checking the patient's vitals on the monitor and writing on a clipboard.
Medical personnel communicating via headset while monitoring the patient.
Overhead view from inside the helicopter, showing the patient and medical personnel, with a view of green fields and a river below.
Medical personnel continuing to monitor the patient and document observations.
Medical personnel communicating via headset and pointing at the patient monitor.
Medical personnel communicating on the radio and listening intently.
One medical personnel writing on a clipboard and the other attending to the patient.
Close-up of the medical personnel writing on a clipboard and interacting with the patient.
Medical personnel speaking into their headset while observing the patient and writing.
Medical personnel with a masked face is talking on radio and making notes.
Medical personnel looking at the patient monitor and making notes.
Medical personnel showing a peace sign and giving a thumbs up to the camera.
Medical personnel looking at the monitor and then at the camera, then continuing to write.
Medical personnel making notes on a clipboard and then looking out the window.
Medical personnel turning to show the clipboard and then looking back to their work.
Medical personnel adjusting equipment on the ceiling of the helicopter.
Medical personnel adjusting the patient's blankets and then returning to their notes.
View from the window showing the vast landscape below, with fields, roads, and a river.
Medical personnel checking the patient and communicating through the headset.
Medical personnel explaining something to the patient and looking out the window.
Medical personnel preparing an IV bag.
Aerial view of the landscape from the helicopter window, showing fields, roads, and a river from a higher altitude.
